rows.label: campfev11_530_175_msg0001
rows.name:
We just need to get across Dannagh
Desert and we'll be in Aurium right?

rows.label: campfev11_530_175_msg0002
rows.name:
Right. The desert is a harsh place,
but the palace is always visible.
You can use it to orient yourself.

rows.label: campfev11_530_175_msg0003
rows.name:
It must be pretty enormous for us to be
able to see it from such a distance...

rows.label: campfev11_530_175_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't try looking up when you're
standing right in front of it, is all
I'll say!

rows.label: campfev11_530_175_msg0005
rows.name:
Iiran technology represents the high
watermark in many domains.

rows.label: campfev11_530_175_msg0006
rows.name:
This type of sky-scraping architecture
is just one example.

rows.label: campfev11_530_175_msg0007
rows.name:
Yeah? Then what's Adel doing with
such a teeny little place back in Aletta?
